//Recommended club Activity Club Calculator 1) Manually enter the angle to target or press the angle button next to the text field to use the device's hardware to get the angle to the target. 

2) Enter the distance to the target as measured by a laser range finder. 

3) Press "Calculate Best Club" to see the best club based on the angle and distance. Distance to Target (yds): Angle to Target (deg): *note: - for downhill, + for uphill Capture Angle w/ Phone Calculate Best Club
