//About Activity About HillCaddy Developed by Clint Wojtowicz 

I can be reached at clint.wojtowicz@gmail.com with any questions or comments. The app was designed and tested using a Samsung Galaxy S5, if there are compatibility issues with your device, please send me an email with a description of the issue. Special thanks to: 

 -Matt Pianowski for drawing the logo. 

 -Peter Ligotti at Callaway for his suggestion to use the accelerometer for angle capture. 

 -The Integrated Systems team at Callaway for their UI design advice and for allowing me to use their Foresight GC2 to capture shot data. 

 -Dr. Charles De Leone at Cal State San Marcos for his advice and mentoring throughout the project. 

 -My Dad for constantly asking how far uphill and downhill shots will play which lead me to the idea for the app.
